Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的第18個夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對身為重考生的我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是不是夏天都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次等重要的還是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成績一直都沒什麼進步耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼沮喪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個夏天努力用功的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋天就一定能看到成果的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為夏天是關鍵時刻嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，本須和，加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕…裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件泳裝你覺得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是為了今天而買的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很…很合適啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常合適
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是個大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，ちぃ衣服換好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的到海邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是個重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的能待在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模擬考成績拿 D 的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貧窮又無暇的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，本須和，加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，週末海邊見囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保應該已經跟你說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三天兩夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定也會去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒那個錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國分寺他說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每年的這個時候\N都會到海邊的別墅去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們要跟他一起同行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以是免費的喔，免費的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,免費…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不過我們可是重考生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能去海邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ泳裝穿這件好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的舊衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐我也邀請了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，那女孩叫裕美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都說要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，本須和先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克服夏天考驗吧，重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是電腦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，跟裕美\N還有清水老師打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是中午吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用白天的打招呼法，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，ちぃ真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還要杵在那裡多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊玩的時間會被耗光的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去幫幫本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多水
