Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要不要一起去玩水？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
