Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像是小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼難得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好好享受怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呸，好…好鹹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你要東張西望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海水是鹹的，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹹水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了\N電腦碰到鹽水不會有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦都有做日常防水\N所以沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長對電腦也很溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢潑我水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起游到那裡去？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不勉強你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我可不會讓你溜掉的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚…晚上嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你上特別課程
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會有間別墅在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你家果然真有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是那個對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的私人海灘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒人來這裡玩罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，檢測結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會不會打擾到你們了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家吵吵鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實是有點吵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年的確比較熱鬧呢\N稔少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過偶而這樣也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都到了這裡，不需要看書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來玩吧！來玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去囉，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,球，秀樹給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的幸福應該就是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不錯的轉換心情方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我可沒忘記要用功喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經打算今夏要\N從早到晚苦讀了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著來玩撲克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得清水老師的房間應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上我會幫你上特別課程
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的課程是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一段夏季的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門沒鎖，請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人缺席吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也拿去抹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦用的防腐蝕膏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為海風、鹽水跟沙粒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都算是精密儀器的天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好還是抹一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，不是有日常防水了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是幫她保養一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,均勻的塗抹在全身就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,均勻的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我抹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫ちぃ抹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3、2、1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辦…辦不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我怎麼辦得到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就教她自己塗抹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先將防護膏像這樣擠出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和先生\N要不要我來幫忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那是貝類，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝類，那這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，那也是貝類
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝類，這也是貝類嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會走的貝類？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，這個叫什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是寄居蟹啦，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔對喔，叫寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那叫寄居蟹喔，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在教她詞句嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ現在還有很多事不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果不教她的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是昆布嗎？\N不，是裙帶菜嗎？還是海藻？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫海草不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海草，那是海草，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是海草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我也來幫忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，拜…拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好睏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是海豚耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海…海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海豚，是海豚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳的眼力真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有海豚耶，海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠們偶而會來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，這不是很棒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只在電視上看過海豚耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也只在水族館看過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，這裡也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點遠\N不過真的有看到對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能近一點看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會不會游到這附近來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到近，如果游到這種近海來\N不就回不去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過很少有這種機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真想多看一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就游到外面一點去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒多遠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學…學長，難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你說不會游泳\N不是開玩笑的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幹嘛拿這個來開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好歹也會蛙式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任誰都有擅長\N與不擅長的東西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嗎，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯考不考游泳這科目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹不會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣很厲害嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹很厲害嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私人遊艇耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然覺得有點火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世界這樣真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會很不公平嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要觀賞海豚\N這一帶是最佳地點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個妳有看到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹看到海豚的“嘩啦”\N會很高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:18:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也要來嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡？在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，還不快去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，反正她有日常防水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼深的地方\N日常防水一點用也沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不會游泳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國分寺的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，學長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這麼亂來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，不經思索就跳下去救人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真像你的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從表面看來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像也沒進水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你在生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ做錯事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會生氣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真是台不可思議的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般如果掉到海裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會進水，然後會很難修復
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果ちぃ發生事情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許會變得更麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救本須和起來的可是ちぃ喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2、2…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的夏天結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次等重要的還是用功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個夏天是關鍵時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標是成績進步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成績竟然又退步了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，夏天熱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，夏天真熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.47,0:23:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個人昏沉沉的，一點精神都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.10,0:24:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天要用蚊香嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蚊香的味道\N可說是夏天的必需品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天清水老師會來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.35,0:24:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.25,0:24:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天還是清水老師最棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.12,0:24:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，招待」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.99,0:24:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.09,0:24:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
